<aka>Pi̱ki Chihowa chia hosh</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Pi̱ki Chihowa chia hosh
 Hatak yoshoba pia ha̱,
 Okcha̱ya na biliashke,
 Ish pim aiahni pulla tok.

[V2]
 Chiso holitopa yokʋt
 Ilap im issish fehna ka
 Ant isht pi chumpa hatok a̱
 E chi aiokpahanchishke.

[V3]
 Ʋno a̱ ik sa̱ yimmi cha,
 A̱ shakba pohloma hoka
 Ant a̱sha na biliashke,
 Ish pim aiahni pulla tok.

[V4]
 Shilombish Holitopa yʋt
 Pi chu̱kʋsh a̱ himonʋchit,
 Pi yohbichi yoke, ahnit,
 E chi aiokpahanchashke.

[V5]
 Enchil ʋhleha moyuma
 Chi̱ bili̱ka aiasha kʋt
 Hatak puyuta aienʋt,
 Pit chi aiokpahanchashke</lyrics>
<title>Praise or Salvation ƲIT3</title>
<time_sig>L.M. (8.8.8.8.)</time_sig>
</song>